The paper deals with designing optimal mechanisms for selling information, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of linear programming to compute the optimal mechanisms suggests that the paper may also belong to the data structures (cs.DS) category. The paper's focus on designing simple and efficient mechanisms for selling information suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. Finally, the paper's emphasis on revenue extraction suggests that it may also belong to the electronic commerce (cs.EC) category.
